sequenceDiagram
  participant U as User (Browser)
  participant FE as Frontend
  participant SF as Supabase Functions
  participant DB as Postgres DB
  participant EX as External API

  U->>FE: ricerca bando / upload pdf
  FE->>SF: invoke parse-bando (file url / id)
  SF->>EX: chiamata API parsing/AI
  EX-->>SF: risultato parsing
  SF->>DB: salva record/metadata
  SF->>FE: ritorna risultato
  FE-->>U: mostra risultato
